\;E\;
\;x\in E\;\;\exists\,a,b,c\in\Bbb C\;\;s.t.
x=au+bf(u)+cf(v)\implies f(x)=f(au)+bf^2u+cf^v=f(au)\implies
x-au\in\ker f=\langle f(u)\rangle\implies x=au+tf(u)\;,\;\;t\in\Bbb C
